articles.title: Europe's Vega-C rocket launches Earth-observation satellite on 1st liftoff since 2022 failure (video) - Space.com
articles.description: The Vega-C bounced back with a launch success today (Dec. 5).
articles.content:
Europe's Vega-C rocket returned to flight Thursday (Dec. 5) with a successful mission, two years after suffering a catastrophic failure.
